| Domain                 | Impact Description                                                                 | Supporting Evidence                                                                                       |
|------------------------|------------------------------------------------------------------------------------|----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------|
| Wealth & Homeownership | Reduced property value appreciation; limited wealth accumulation for minorities   | 52% less wealth gain in redlined areas over 40 years ([Qrius, 2020](https://qrius.com/what-is-redlining-and-how-does-it-affect-urban-communities/)) |
